main event: An observer reported seeing a long, cigar-shaped dark object flying over Dayton, Ohio, on June 13, 1968.
interesting points: The object was described as very dark and approximately several hundred feet in length., The object moved toward the southwest with no visible means of propulsion., It emitted a humming sound, similar to a generator., Lights at the base of the object gave off a greenish hue., The phenomenon was sighted from an apartment, and the observer was watching TV at the time.
witness description: The witness is a 66-year-old male who reported the sighting.
